Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候起  我就時常能看到奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概是被稱作是妖怪一類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你往哪踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  危險  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目摔下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  那邊是別人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  麻煩你撿下球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球  球…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張臉  是夏目大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳在你身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  追上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  這繩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來以前好像也有過這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帳交出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳  快交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被妖怪纏上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事幹就跟著來了  你就這德行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老  老師  很難受啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶  蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帳交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我…  很難受啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是幹什麼吧  蠢貓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你說過我不是貓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以招財貓為憑依的暫時的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你是保鏢吧  那就認真點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別把我當普通保鏢使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了得到友人帳而在等你壽命終結
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用重新解釋  你這大福餅貓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  總有一天我要吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
