Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是心地善良的藤原夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志  吃飯囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵吉還沒回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它沒來吃飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在外面吃過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了它就會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個好吃  是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是百合根啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不給他們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看見妖怪的事絕對要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒回房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我打得太用力了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓  貓咪老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我啊  你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼弄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拿你的髒爪子到處踩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  洗不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹了什麼啊  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我剛才打了你  鬧彆扭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  剛才是老師你不對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只黑的是啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這傢伙是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  不是老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一目瞭然吧  呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉盤這麼大的貓沒幾隻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這傢伙是變成老師的樣子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的何在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  友人帳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  跑哪去了  那只黑貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  這麼黑可找不到那黑傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  友人帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人類晚上在外面晃很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今晚的空氣好像跟平常不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找一會  再讓我找一會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那上面有妖怪們重要的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:06:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻滾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  冷靜下來夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然友人帳被搶很讓人生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我感覺那只黑貓沒有惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才鬆懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在吵吵鬧鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓別的妖怪知道友人帳被搶了會更麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐火？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量不少啊  這是要去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像聞到  有人類的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老 老師  好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍一忍  用我的味道掩蓋過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想著是不是人  這是野獸的腥臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說是腥臭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼高貴而偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  以前主人經常帶著人的味道回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人化成人的樣子去村裏玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還帶些好吃的回來分給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的人類  跟他們扯上關係就沒好下場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是斑大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這身姿何時看都是這麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你是紅峰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您正在用餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請務必分我一點殘羹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這張臉好像在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目玲子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子  聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是夏目玲子的孫子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅峰  剛才那群妖怪是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是森林裏的妖怪聚集起來開宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  你在這附近見過一隻叼著一疊紙的可愛黑貓沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  倒是有只大頭肥貓往宴會場去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…肥貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅峰小姐  能帶我們去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認真的嗎  人類的孩子去了立刻就會被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就裝成妖怪去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  我必須得找到那隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這任性的眼神  的確是像玲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是喜歡他這點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊  再廢話就吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我就帶你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能順利裝成妖怪也行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到時候你被認出來是人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當大家的下酒菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！斑大人變成豆丁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒是在這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是去喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  夏目少爺得化妝或是戴面具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人也不能露出野獸的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟您很有名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目玲子把友人帳傳給了長得像她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著野獸的少年這事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到處都在傳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你想讓那孩子在家待多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊  哥哥也說他不願意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你回來啦  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  找到玲子阿姨的遺物了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的祖母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這是什麼  塗鴉本？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她是個怪人  看來相當怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個扔掉也可以哦  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西留著也沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天生擁有強大妖力的祖母玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將打敗的妖怪的名字寫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂立了主從契約
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候  我一點都不知道友人帳和玲子祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人就以這副樣子去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  紅峰  來得真遲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不解風情  我化了個妝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  沒見過的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是我帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩啊  也讓我們加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  來來  喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我說你  有點人類的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我想起主人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  主人也老是帶著人類的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡人類的森林之主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他變成人的樣子去村裏玩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩到捕狐貍的陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從被一個獵人救了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就經常變成人去見那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還為交到了人類朋友而雀躍不已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那位大人妖力雖然強大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭腦卻不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會想和人類交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  還跟那個夏目玲子比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  有誰在附近看到一隻黑貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多來談談那件事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到可惡人類封印主人的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是復仇的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人將力量分給下等的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓我們住在這森林裏的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  我們就進行夜襲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類根本不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起進攻他們就不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜襲是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人襲擊了家畜  所以被人類封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是終於找到封印地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個高高的紅牆房子的地板下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也沒必要襲擊那房子裏的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒必要  不過看這些傢伙喝成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知會做出什麼事來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你  可別去多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個數量是無法輕易阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  你就別管他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正人類能做到的事也是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還好  我能聽見你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能聽到他們的聲音  還有人類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分厚薄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就一點忙也幫不上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟玲子不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子真難懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底喜歡他哪一點？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感興趣的是友人帳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕緊把他吃掉  搶過來不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也能給我殺殺時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生很短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓到它了  老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  這傢伙怎麼這麼老實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只黑貓會不會是故意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得它是想通過搶友人帳  把我們帶到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅峰  你辦得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感應一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是強大的妖怪被封印在某個憑依上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:16:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑依啊  這樣做很流行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這妖氣… 很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難道是主人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可憐了  可惡的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封印了卻還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高的紅牆房子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候弄斷的繩子是這只黑貓的結界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅峰小姐  趕快通知大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人這個樣子  誰都不會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把封印解開  恢復以前的樣子才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有個低級妖怪說這傢伙跟玲子比賽過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  聽說是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個  或許是因為名字被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它才無法打破封印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把名字還給它的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過問題在於名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝在憑依裏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳是不會自動搜索名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅峰小姐  主人的名字叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  我也只知道叫他主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  我一定會把名字還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請你幫忙阻止大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個  在這裏幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發  是要去襲擊人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人已經回到這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  呆子  別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰知道主人的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道了名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人類的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  該死的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開他！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了  滾一邊去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意聽  這其中應該會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會有知道主人名字的妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貍追大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貍追  我把名字還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貍追大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主…人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你而能活動了的我  去找他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生真短暫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點明白為什麼大家會說我笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會搶友人帳？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回到森林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪們正想為我去襲擊人類的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有力量阻止  就把你帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你應該能做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印你的也是人類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻想要阻止妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不會再到人類的村子裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了啊  黑貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑貓咪真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你以為是靠了誰這次的事件才能解決的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  斑大人的傷也不礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是無法喜歡人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想著為了斑大人  就找機會把你給吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻礙於主人的大恩不能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人  要不乾脆就跟我一起回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我還是暫時待在這傢伙身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那一眨眼的功夫過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坦率起來還真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的煩惱是  小小的離別帶來的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間的邂逅與分別
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一個一個的剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好珍惜起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:50.91,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,550)}融化在春天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫玄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  請幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是芝原野的石像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是有兩座的  還有一座怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠…  她已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

